properties.areaDesc: Los Angeles County San Fernando Valley; Santa Clarita Valley
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 11 at 2:05PM PST until January 11 at 11:00PM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 15 to 25 mph with gusts up to 40 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Santa Clarita Valley and San Fernando Valley.

* WHEN...Until 11 PM PST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and
make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Local gusts to 45 mph across the Santa
Clarita Valley.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 6 PM UNTIL 11 PM PST THIS EVENING
